        <img src="/images/publicrecipe.png" alt="Publish your recipe for free" loading="lazy" class="flex items-center justify-center w-full md:w-9/12 lg:w-7/12 xl:w-6/12 h-full">
        <div class="my-10 font-medium text-center space-y-7">
            <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-slate-200">Publish your recipe now!</h1>
